## LEGO Re-Design Concept

### Concept Overview
| **Aspect**          | **Details**                                                                                                                |
|----------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Folder**           | SEE Lego sketches folder                                                                                                  |
| **Description**      | I am exploring the creation of a **non-conventional LEGO piece** that moves beyond standard rectangular geometry by **incorporating curved or angled forms**. This concept is **inspired by LEGO Flower Bouquet sets**, which demonstrate how expressive, organic shapes can still exist within the LEGO system. |

---

### Goals
| **Key Target**          | **Details**                                                                                  |
|--------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **1. Non-Rectangular Geometry** | Introduce organic forms like curves, arcs, or angled pieces.                         |
| **2. System Compatibility**   | Ensure compatibility with existing LEGO pieces, keeping clutch power and interlocking integrity. |
| **3. Creative Expression**    | Enable more creative and sculptural builds while maintaining practicality.              |

---

